  "title": "Clinic Assistant (Patient Service & Clinical Support)",
  "description": "<p><u>Job Description:</u></p><p>Clinic Assistants support patient service, treatment programme management, and clinical operations under doctor supervision. Responsibilities include coordinating appointments and ensuring treatment frequency follows the doctor-prescribed regimen.</p><p>Clinics are located island-wide, including Central Area medical centres next to MRT stations such as Scotts Medical Centre, Novena Medical Centre, and Raffles Place.</p><p><u>Key Responsibilities:</u></p><p>- Patient reception and appointment coordination</p><p>- Treatment programme scheduling based on doctor instructions</p><p>- Assisting doctors during consultations and treatments</p><p>- Supporting medical and wellness therapies, including post-treatment care</p><p>- Preparing treatment rooms and maintaining clinical hygiene</p><p>- Updating patient records and supporting daily clinic operations</p><p><u>Requirements:</u></p><p>- Minimum GCE O-Level or Polytechnic Diploma</p><p>- Preferably in medical, allied health, biomedical, or hospitality fields</p><p>- Medical clinic experience preferred</p><p>- Willingness to learn and work in a clinical environment<br /><br /><u>What we offer:</u><br /><br />· An attractive Salary Package with fixed pay and Monthly Performance Bonus.</p><p>· 5 working days per week</p><p>· Fast-track career path for fast learners and high performers.</p><p>· Opportunity to work alongside doctors and management.</p><p>· Reward and recognition program that appreciates the most competent and brightest employees.</p><p>· Promotion based on performance and achievements.</p><p>· Generous package of free\nmedical aesthetics treatments (up to S$6000 per year) selecting from 100+ treatments for full time employees.</p><p>· Exclusive staff discounts on our products and services.</p><p>· Medical Benefits for full time employees.<br /><br /><strong>Application:</strong><br /><a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><u>Complete the form before applying:</u><br /></a><a href=\"https://forms.gle/BANHb1kAYwBY7k6D8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://forms.gle/BANHb1kAYwBY7k6D8</a></p><p>Pay package within the stated range will be commensurate with relevant experience and educational qualifications.<br /></p><p>Please be advised that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"></a></p>",
